Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:20.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:25.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:32.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:35.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:41.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:45.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:53.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:03.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:09.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:14.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:21.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:26.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:31.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:33.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:37.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:42.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:20.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}爱太过沉重而拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:25.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}由爱生恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:27.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}任何事都是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:32.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}尴尬的事由总被掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:35.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}这伪善者的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}在扭曲的泥沼时代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:41.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}本已约定的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:45.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也不觉擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:53.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}彼此伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}抛开原有的理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}莫非这就是末路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:03.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不认同命运 奋起反抗之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:09.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}也无法逃离坠落时的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:14.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}Ah 多少次我都能寻到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:21.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你的瞳眸 温暖的手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:24.49,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}「爱永远只能给我伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:26.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}你喃喃自语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:31.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}是否曾因害怕相信而哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:33.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}承认脆弱 变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:37.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}不再畏惧 努力相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:42.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3a&HFF}{\4a&H3F}定能找到真爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验体E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑量子波施行手术 完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:08.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入术后过程观察
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋里 有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.18,0:00:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人吗 能听到我的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.13,0:01:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在对我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你能听到我的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:07.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪 你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就在你面前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 能说话好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.13,0:01:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是谁 为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连名字都想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我给你取个名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就叫阿勒路亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒路亚?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是感谢上帝的词语哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢? 感谢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还用问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是活着了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那对我来说 是名副其实的洗礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:52.30,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}{\pos(162,110)}{\3a&HC9&\4c&H000000&\1c&HFEFDFF&}战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.20,0:03:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有阻止了5年前阿撒迪斯坦的内乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不引发战争就阻止了内乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为那种行为非常伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别提这些了 今后你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回阿撒迪斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安局会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦可能以你为口实加以介入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没加入联邦的阿撒迪斯坦被世界舍弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.09,0:04:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经济崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保守派领导人拉撒去世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:38.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和改革派的纷争也深陷泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因如此我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密的航向转向阿撒迪斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问个无聊的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位是恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女的直觉猜错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎还没打算穿上制服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 命中率是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,78% 78%
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法像哥哥一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫菲尔德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常感觉到你的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德喜欢洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔德喜欢洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 嗯 知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不介意的话我来者不拒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意的话之后去房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了 被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让她清醒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可受不了被人比较
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}{\pos(365,367)}阿拉伯海  海上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俘虏的Gundam机师被救走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还被KATARON抢先一步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失态啊 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错看了天人的战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不听借口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS不需要无能的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林特少校 下次作战你来负责
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:06:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我教你A-LAWS的做法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请指教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅长扫荡作战的阿尔巴·林特少校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟把那个恶名昭彰的男人招来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据保安局人员的证言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam似乎将收监中的阿撒迪斯坦皇女带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说Gundam机师中有中东出身的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了年轻貌美的公主 想当白马骑士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推测现在的天人会徇私情而行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援救机师同伴就是最好的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.84,0:07:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这一带撒网比较妥当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许使用Trilobite
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:59.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}（Trilobite：联邦新型MA，搭载伪太阳炉，可水下作业）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事 本次作战希望他也能参加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到5分钟的闪电作战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让舰船沉入海中引发海啸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扰乱部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时增加周围湿度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使粒子武器的效果减半
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上4架Gundam的合作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种大胆而不失缜密的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在哪儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite? 资料上的新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然开发出了搭载GN Drive的MA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听闻有某位女性捐赠了大笔款项
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好事之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4小队受令转移到地上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿勒威准尉 请立即到舰桥来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队 出击准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-1发来了情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来果然去阿撒迪斯坦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要做吗 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天人是我们达到目的所必须的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且帮助他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能保护玛莉娜公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会 把你重要的朋友救出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说要离开王宫…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 按照现在联邦政府的政策
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国就算加盟联邦也没有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:10:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就要用我的方式创造这个国家的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.42,0:10:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阿撒迪斯坦就无法实现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是重建这个国家还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯 让我也和部队同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会碍事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:27.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该也有能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 和我一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阿撒迪斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想重建国家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造一个没有纷争 大家都能和平生活的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你也能帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做的 只有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.83,0:10:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这么悲伤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 战争不能孕育任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能让人失去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在进入天人之前 我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也有些东西是从破坏中诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用Gundam来斩断世界的扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我和Gundam的战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深度固定在3200
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 没问题吗 让我看到这种机密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手不够 你不是有宇宙技师的资格认定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不劳动者不得食
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 请问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫伊安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安·巴斯汀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊安先生 你为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看腻了战场 想消除战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的人都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被送去战场最前线的  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被军方改造了身体的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在恐怖袭击中失去亲人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有被游击队利用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在战争中失去了重要之物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是世界的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我们是罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会接受惩罚 等战争消除之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索玛·比利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得是人革的超兵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么就没发觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够那样介入我脑量子波的只有玛丽而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:13:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被联合国军抓住时 我以为赎罪的时刻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想就那么死了也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想救回玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方可是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 你把超人机关的设施…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我杀了同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.85,0:13:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽若是知道了 一定会恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确做了该被她恨的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使被人怨恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知我的战斗会不会有这样的理由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是赞同伊欧利亚的计划才加入的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 曾经也想消除纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但除此之外 我还想抹消自己可憎的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憎的过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是怀着这种心情来战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我的自私使众多生命牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我没能抹消过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我没有战斗的理由 没有待在这里的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你有理由待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你为什么救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能找到战斗的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios的后继机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用这架机体 这架Gundam 救回玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使哈雷路亚已死 无法使用脑量子波
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的我一定会断然否定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 克莉丝 理坦 莫雷诺医生…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能再次鼓起勇气面对世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 保护最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃米利奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 即将穿过霍尔木兹海峡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:22.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（霍尔木兹海峡：连接阿拉伯海与波斯湾的海峡）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周边太安静了 连鱼都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个深度…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E声纳有反应 6个敌人高速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是鱼雷 菲尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field 最大幅度展开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌袭?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼雷里有重化合物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声纳失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这深度敌人还能动?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型机?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在预定地点拖住敌舰 发射「虎子」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去舰船中央
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波来袭 大型鱼雷两发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field被突破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下部集装箱进水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算Gundam出击 在这个深度…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密上浮 到Gundam能出击的深度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上来的炸弹 估计使用的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化学炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两分钟的轰炸之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以Trilobite进行近战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜不能看到敌舰被压毁的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林特少校 索敌和初期行动很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 对方指挥官会如何应对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船体覆盖了树脂 炮门打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操舵也不行 可恶 敌人在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E声纳无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰炸很快就会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后海中的敌人就会接近我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动直接攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人突击船体左舷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受损甚大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 有可能被压毁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法探测的敌人就在面前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密又到达了Gundam出击深度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:18:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且敌人还帮我们缩短了下部集装箱的注水时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭MS的推力还想对抗Trilobite
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀手锏在此 TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在水中 只要够近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉开距离 用鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 驱逐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.33,0:18:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起来吧 去阿撒迪斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱逐目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 冲出海面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.02,0:19:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 Trilobite竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.78,0:19:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰艇后退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动MS队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Ahead是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的新型
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这动作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个难缠的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:20:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那招式 不会错 就是那时的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等侥幸 不枉我忍辱偷生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这机体 实验体E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是机体的问题 是我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是 KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府组织吗 别挡我的路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退重整旗鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝交手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让我受益匪浅啊 少校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反政府组织KATARON
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有这等战力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是谁呢 说想见我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉娜·伊斯迈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳·巴赫蒂亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是KATARON成员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对地球联邦做法的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:47.38,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}純真さがシンプルな力に変わる時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:52.52,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:59.92,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ガラスケースに横たわる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:07.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:10.75,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}振り上げた手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.07,0:22:14.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:18.25,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}落ちるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.33,0:22:23.51,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}しゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:31.17,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Prototype boy　明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:38.78,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}語り継ぐような美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:49.75,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}この体を失いそうなギリギリの場所が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:56.35,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:47.38,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}纯真化作纯粹的力量时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:52.52,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}在世间映出条条斜影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:59.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}玻璃柜中慵懒的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:07.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是那般不可捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:14.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}扬起的手 无法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:23.51,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如陷落般 屈身蜷伏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:31.17,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Prototype boy 穿过明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:38.78,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}虽无法传为美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:49.75,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}这生死一线之间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:56.35,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}却这样可悲地与我相衬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.18,0:23:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于下定决心了吗 毕利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要承蒙照顾了 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里要叫我司令
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你继承已故艾佛曼教授的事业
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担任新型MS开发主任
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.23,0:23:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:30.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尺寸不合 太紧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就准备别的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.05,0:23:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是性骚扰 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.24,0:23:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇·李·诺列嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九条 你从很久以前就一直在利用我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且践踏了我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS残酷的攻击折磨着Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而刹那在红莲之火中遭遇戏剧性的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.90,0:24:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 故国燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.46,0:24:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重逢似猛药


